snippet.title: BattleHeights Party Game [STEAM trailer]
snippet.description:
BattleHeights is a multiplayer Heroic Fantasy PARTY Game. Choose your class, use your double jump, leap from cloud to cloud like an eagle in dizzying battles where the void becomes as perilous as it is strategic.

⇨ Discord: https://discord.gg/hunbEKkauV
⇨ Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2932940/BattleHeights
